        "content": "<p>Environments:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>linux: <a href=\"https://github.com/Rust-for-Linux/linux/tree/f26449565019315650c9fe87743b10103910ca6b\">Current latest rust-next tree</a></li>\n<li>toolchains: stable-aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu</li>\n<li>rust-analyzer: Visual Studio Code extension, version 0.4.2471</li>\n<li>All actions are performed inside a Docker container based on <code>rust:1.87.0-bookworm</code> (not sure if this is relevant)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Hi! I've generated <code>rust-project.json</code> using <code>make LLVM=1 rust-analyzer</code>, but rust-analyzer fails with the following error.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"mi\">2025</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">05</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">24</span><span class=\"n\">T14</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">56</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"mf\">53.110157159</span><span class=\"n\">Z</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ERROR</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">FetchWorkspaceError</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">analyzer</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">failed</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">to</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">load</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">workspace</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Failed</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">to</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">load</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">project</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">root</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">workspace</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">project</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">json</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Failed</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">to</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">deserialize</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">json</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">root</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">workspace</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">project</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">json</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Invalid</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">cfg</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"--edition=2024\"</span><span class=\"p\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">value</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">should</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">be</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">quotes</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">line</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">7</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">column</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">13</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Here is a snippet from the generated <code>rust-project.json</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"crates\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"s\">\"cfg\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"s\">\"no_fp_fmt_parse\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"s\">\"--edition=2024\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"p\">],</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"s\">\"deps\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[],</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"s\">\"display_name\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"core\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"s\">\"edition\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"2021\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"s\">\"env\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"s\">\"RUST_MODFILE\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"This is only for rust-analyzer\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"p\">},</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"s\">\"is_proc_macro\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">false</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"s\">\"is_workspace_member\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">false</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"s\">\"root_module\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"/usr/local/rustup/toolchains/stable-aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu/lib/rustlib/src/rust/library/core/src/lib.rs\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">},</span>\n<span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>If I remove <code>\"--edition=2024\"</code> from the <code>cfg</code> array, it works fine. But if feels like a workaround rather than a proper solution. Any help or guidance would be appreciated!</p>\n<p>UPDATE:<br>\nI think this problem is related to commit fffcd7ce47888c9f6d90f9fe803d0fc288b35fb2 (rust: compile libcore with edition 2024 for 1.87+), since it changes <code>rust/Makefile</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ifeq</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"cp\">$(</span><span class=\"n\">call</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rustc</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">min</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">version</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">108700</span><span class=\"p\">),</span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">core</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">cfgs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">+=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">--</span><span class=\"n\">edition</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">2024</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">else</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">core</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">cfgs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">+=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">--</span><span class=\"n\">edition</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">2021</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">endif</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
